content.html: For the past week, I've been going crazy rebuilding a *better* version of an AWS service. Something that I had in mind for over 2 years. If it works, I'll open source it. If not, I had a lot of fun. The ability to build is magic, and the freedom to build is a bless.
content.value:
For the past week, I've been going crazy rebuilding a *better* version of an AWS service. Something that I had in mind for over 2 years.

If it works, I'll open source it. If not, I had a lot of fun.

The ability to build is magic, and the freedom to build is a bless.
